name: The Teeniest Hokusai - pixelart of "The Great Wave off Kanagawa" by Hokusai - by Lorem Ipsum
description: A 4096 x 4096 pixel upscaled (from 16 x 16) tribute to Hokusai (1760 - 1849) and his iconic woodblock print "The Great Wave off Kanagawa". This was made in memory of the first HEN swap contract exploit and the "great wave" it caused.
